## ✅ Tailwind CSS Fixed!

Perfect! Tailwind CSS is now working correctly. The issue was that in Tailwind v4, the configuration needs to explicitly define color mappings to CSS custom properties.

### **What I Fixed:**

1. **Updated Tailwind v4 Configuration**: Added proper color definitions in the `tailwind.config.ts` that map to the CSS custom properties defined in `globals.css`

2. **CSS Variable Mapping**: The config now properly maps Tailwind utilities like `bg-background`, `border-border`, etc. to the CSS variables defined in the design system
